
 AtmCashDispenserSystem Notes
 ----------------------

 Functional Requirements/Acceptance criteria
 --------------------------------------------
  1. user should pass the amount & get the cash for that if certain denominations or balance is available in atm
  2. system has 3 denominations currently i.e 2000, 500, 100. But it can be extensible so design in that way
  3. if specific cash req is not available then return false or say. amount cant be processed.



  amount -> AtmCashDispenserService -> handler(chain of handler starts with highest denomination handler)